Option 1 – Temporarily stop this DC from advertising SYSVOL (recommended)

On the problematic DC:

reg add HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\Netlogon\Parameters /v SysVolReady /t REG_DWORD /d 0 /f
net stop netlogon
net start netlogon


This tells the domain:

“This DC is not ready to serve SYSVOL.”

Now:

DFS referrals will go only to serv2 / serv3

GPMC will work immediately

Users will get correct policies

DFSR can continue rebuilding in the background

Once the state becomes 4, revert it:

reg add HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\Netlogon\Parameters /v SysVolReady /t REG_DWORD /d 1 /f
net stop netlogon
net start netlogon
